  "plan": "## OpenCRAVAT GenePattern Module — Implementation Plan\n\n### 1. Overview\nOpenCRAVAT is a GenePattern module that <img src\\=\"https\\://opencravat.org/images/OpenCRAVAT_Logo-0-sm.png\" width\\=50px alt\\=\"img\"/>OpenCRAVAT performs genomic variant interpretation including variant impact, annotation, and scoring.\n\n### 2. Parameters\nThe module exposes 20 parameters:\n- Required: input.file, cravat.username, cravat.password, assembly\n- Optional: variants, cancer, clinical.relevance, dbnsfp, denovo, evolution, genes, genomic.features, germline, interactions, literature, multiplex.assays, noncoding, populations, protein.visualization, variant.effect.prediction\n\n### 3. Command Line\n```\npython /opencravat/opencravat_command_line.py -i <input.file> -user <cravat.username> -pass <cravat.password> -assembly <assembly> <variants> <cancer> <clinical.relevance> <dbnsfp> <denovo> <evolution> <genes> <genomic.features> <germline> <interactions> <literature> <multiplex.assays> <noncoding> <populations> <protein.visualization>  <variant.effect.prediction>\n```\n\n### 4. Docker Image\nDocker image: genepattern/opencravat\\:0.4\n\n### 5. Validation Strategy\n- Validate all required parameters are provided\n- Validate file formats match expected extensions\n- Check parameter value ranges where applicable\n\n### 6. Implementation Roadmap\nPhase 1: Wrapper script implementation\nPhase 2: Docker container setup\nPhase 3: Parameter validation and error handling\nPhase 4: Testing and documentation",
  "wrapper_script": "opencravat_command_line.py",
  "command_line": "python /opencravat/opencravat_command_line.py -i <input.file> -user <cravat.username> -pass <cravat.password> -assembly <assembly> <variants> <cancer> <clinical.relevance> <dbnsfp> <denovo> <evolution> <genes> <genomic.features> <germline> <interactions> <literature> <multiplex.assays> <noncoding> <populations> <protein.visualization>  <variant.effect.prediction>",
